---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="About - Meshum"
	description="Learn about Meshum's mission to unblock software teams by connecting their scattered knowledge."
>
	<Hero
		title="Unblocking teams through"
		highlight="connected knowledge"
		subtitle="We're building the knowledge layer that software organizations need to move faster without losing context."
		showCTA={false}
	/>

	<!-- Vision Section -->
	<section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-white mb-8">Our Vision</h2>

			<div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-gray leading-relaxed">
				<p>
					Every software organization struggles with the same problem: knowledge is everywhere, but finding it
					is nowhere easy. Documentation lives in Confluence, code in GitHub, tasks in Jira, discussions in
					Slack, and tribal knowledge in people's heads.
				</p>

				<p>
					The result? Developers spend hours in meetings answering the same questions. Architects wait days
					for input from other teams. New hires take weeks to become productive. Critical context gets lost
					between tools.
				</p>

				<p>
					We're building Meshum to fix this. A unified knowledge layer that connects all your existing
					tools—without forcing you to change how you work. Everything becomes searchable. Everything becomes
					queryable. And AI agents that deeply understand each team's domain can answer questions without
					interrupting the humans.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Principles Section -->
	<section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-bg-darker">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-text-white mb-4">Our principles</h2>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
				<div class="p-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-white mb-3">Keep your tools</h3>
					<p class="text-text-gray leading-relaxed">
						We don't believe in rip-and-replace. Your team has invested in Confluence, Notion, GitHub,
						Jira—and they work. Meshum connects to them all, creating value without creating disruption.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-white mb-3">Your data stays yours</h3>
					<p class="text-text-gray leading-relaxed">
						Customer data is isolated per namespace and never shared across tenants. Bring your own LLM
						keys. Self-host if you need to. We're not building a data moat—we're building a tool.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-white mb-3">Domain-scoped AI</h3>
					<p class="text-text-gray leading-relaxed">
						Generic AI assistants hallucinate because they lack context. Meshum's team personas are scoped
						to specific domains and trained on your actual knowledge—so they give accurate, grounded
						answers.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-white mb-3">Async by default</h3>
					<p class="text-text-gray leading-relaxed">
						Meetings are synchronization overhead. We help teams get answers asynchronously—through AI
						agents, through connected search, through workflows that span team boundaries without blocking
						humans.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Security Section -->
	<section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" id="security">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-white mb-8">Security & Privacy</h2>

			<div class="space-y-6">
				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-white mb-2">Tenant Isolation</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-text-gray leading-relaxed">
						Each customer gets isolated namespaces in our Kubernetes cluster. Data never crosses tenant
						boundaries. This applies to both the knowledge graph and all vector embeddings.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-white mb-2">Encryption at Rest</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-text-gray leading-relaxed">
						All stored data is encrypted at the storage layer. We use industry-standard encryption methods
						and follow security best practices.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-white mb-2">BYOK LLM Support</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-text-gray leading-relaxed">
						Don't want your data touching our models? Bring your own Azure OpenAI, Anthropic, or any
						provider endpoint. Your API keys, your compliance requirements, your control.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-white mb-2">Self-Hosted Option</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-text-gray leading-relaxed">
						For organizations that need complete control, Meshum can be deployed in your own infrastructure
						using Docker Compose or Kubernetes. Same features, your environment.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Status Section -->
	<section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-bg-darker">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-white mb-4">Current Status</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-text-gray mb-8">
				We're in early development, finalizing architecture and building the first connectors. If you're
				interested in being an early adopter or design partner, we'd love to talk.
			</p>
			<a
				href="https://github.com/meshum"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				class="btn-secondary inline-flex items-center gap-2"
			>
				<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path
						fill-rule="evenodd"
